<figureCitation box="[160,243,1088,1115]" captionStart="FIGURES 16–19" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1973,1998]" captionTargetBox="[151,1430,177,1954]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[151,1430,177,1954]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 16–19. Habitat of Platambus sawadai group in China. 16. Heishiding, Guangdong; 17. Jinggang Shan, Jiangxi. 18. Tianmu Shan, Zhejiang. 19. Jizu Shan, Yunnan." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3235888/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
