<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="536" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,980,1187]" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1124,1151]" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">Distribution.</emphasis>
Lowland species known so far only from the 
<typeStatus box="[887,935,1125,1151]" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">type</typeStatus>
locality (Dinghu Shan) in 
<collectingRegion box="[1246,1380,1124,1150]" country="China" name="Guangdong" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">Guangdong</collectingRegion>
. The present finding thus represents the second known locality of this species (
<figureCitation box="[975,1060,1160,1187]" captionStart="FIGURE 20" captionStartId="9.[151,250,1256,1281]" captionTargetBox="[163,1427,182,1235]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[151,1435,170,1245]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURE 20. Map of distribution of Platambus sawadai group in China." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3235890/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="536">Fig. 20</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
